CHANGELOG
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
26-10-2003  0.3  - Ability to set fixed color for text
                 - Experimental supprt for implenting images
		   (Currently transparency seems to be ignored)
07-02-2003  0.2  - Position of watermark on image is now configurable
                 - If getMarkedImage is called before an image has been
		   created, a default string will be printed onto the
		   image to prevent errors
02-02-2003  0.1  - Initial release

